headline: Korean Air Selects GE Aerospace Engines to Power New 787-10s and 777-9s
summary: GE Aerospace (NYSE:GE) announced today that following Korean Air's agreement to purchase 20 Boeing 777-9s and up to 30 787-10s, the airline has placed an order for GEnx and GE9X engines to power its new aircraft.
